<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,521,1178,1203]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Pelocoris binotulatus nigriculus</emphasis>
Berg, 1879
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="46.[151,1436,1178,1418]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
Geographical distribution: 
<collectingCountry box="[502,573,1214,1238]" name="Brazil" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[585,667,1214,1238]" name="Bolivia" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Bolivia</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[723,838,1214,1238]" name="Argentina" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Argentina</collectingCountry>
. The recent record from 
<collectingCountry box="[1117,1227,1214,1238]" name="Colombia" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Colombia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Morales-Castano &amp; Molano-Rendon" firstAuthor="Morales-Castano" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" pagination="121 - 128" refId="ref40044" refString="Morales-Castano, I. T. &amp; Molano-Rendon, F. (2008) Heteropteros acuaticos del Quindio (Colombia): los infraordenes Gerromorpha y Nepomorpha. Revista Colombiana de Entomologia, 34, 121 - 128." type="journal article" year="2008">Morales-Castaño &amp; Molano-Rendón 2008</bibRefCitation>
) needs confirmation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="46" pageNumber="47" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="46.[151,1436,1178,1418]" box="[199,985,1286,1310]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
Distribution in 
<collectingCountry box="[370,442,1286,1310]" name="Brazil" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Brazil</collectingCountry>
: Southeast Region (MG) (
<bibRefCitation author="Melo &amp; Nieser" box="[735,973,1286,1310]" firstAuthor="Melo" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" pagination="43 - 49" refId="ref39820" refString="Melo, A. L. &amp; Nieser, N. (2004) Faunistical notes on aquatic and semiaquatic Heteroptera of Minas Gerais (Brazil): an annotated list of Gerromorpha and Nepomorpha collected near Januaria. Lundiana, 5, 43 - 49." type="journal article" year="2004">Melo &amp; Nieser 2004</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="46.[151,1436,1178,1418]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
Comments: This species probably also occurs in Central-West Region (MT, MS). 
<bibRefCitation author="Poi de Neiff" box="[1117,1335,1322,1346]" firstAuthor="Poi de Neiff" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" pagination="55 - 63" refId="ref41777" refString="Poi de Neiff, A. (2003) Macroinvertebrates living on Eichhornia azurea Kunth in the Paraguay River. Acta Limnologica Brasiliensia, 15, 55 - 63." type="journal article" year="2003">Poi de Neiff (2003)</bibRefCitation>
reported the occurrence of the species along the 
<collectingCountry box="[600,704,1359,1383]" name="Paraguay" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Paraguay</collectingCountry>
River, and some of the collecting stations were located on these two Brazilian states.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
